<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"
"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
  <head>
    <link href="files/css/fitnesse.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />

    <title>Two calls during offpeak time only</title>
  </head>

  <body><h1>Two calls during offpeak time only</h1>
  
  <table border="0"
      cellpadding="">
      <tr>
        <td colspan="2">Given the following tariff plans</td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td>Name</td>

        <td>Off-peak Charge per 10 seconds in pence</td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td>Business</td>

        <td>3</td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td>Leisure</td>

        <td>10</td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td>Standard</td>

        <td>7</td>

      </tr>
	  
    </table>
  
  <table border="0"
      cellpadding="">
      <tr>
        <td colspan="3">Given the following customers</td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td>Name</td>

        <td>Phone Number</td>

        <td>Tariff Plan</td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td>Alice</td>

        <td>447712345678</td>

        <td>Leisure</td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td>Bob</td>

        <td>447787654321</td>

        <td>Business</td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td>Carol</td>

        <td>447711223344</td>

        <td>Business</td>
      </tr>
	  
	  <tr>
        <td>Diana</td>

        <td>447744332211</td>

        <td>Standard</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
	
	<table border="0">
      <tr>
        <td colspan="2">Given Peak Period  </td>
      </tr>
	  <tr>
        <td>Start </td>
		<td>End </td>
      </tr>
	  <tr>
        <td>07:00 </td>
		<td>19:00 </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
	
	<table border="0"
      cellpadding="">
      <tr>
        <td colspan="4">Given these calls are made</td>
      </tr>
	  
	  <tr>
        <td>Start time</td>

        <td>From</td>

        <td>To</td>
		
		<td>Duration</td>
      </tr>
	  
	  
	  <tr>
        <td>20:00</td>

        <td>447744332211</td>

        <td>447711223344</td>
		
		<td>30</td>
      </tr>
	  
	  <tr>
        <td>6:49</td>

        <td>447712345678</td>

        <td>447787654321</td>
		
		<td>600</td>
      </tr>
	  
    </table>
    
    <p>The calls are charged based on the percentage in/out of peak time and based on the tariff plan.</p>
  
  <table bgcolor="" border="0">
      <tr>
        <td colspan="2">The charges are</td>
      </tr>
      
      <tr>
        <td>Phone no.</td>
        <td>Total amount</td>
		
      </tr>
	  
	  <tr>
        <td>447744332211</td>
        <td>21</td>
		
      </tr>
	  
	  <tr>
        <td>447712345678</td>
        <td>600</td>
		
      </tr>
 
    </table></body>
</html>
